      <heading>Tue Oct 31 (Dreq)       :: Female Channeler</heading>
      <slot>15</slot>
      <level>193</level>
      <author>0</author>
      <date>0</date>
      <text>*written in a sloppy hand*

Patrol report:
I, Dedicated Dreq Cypher, was in the Oval plaza in Caemlyn for patrol duty.
As I was standing guard, watching the citizens of Caemlyn on their daily
routines, a Gate snapped into existance just outside of the plaza. I could
not see the flows that made up the Gate, so, presumably, it was woven by
a woman with Saidar. A naked, dirty and wounded woman flew out from the
Gate with tremendous force, and if I were not there to catch the woman
with flows of air, she might have died from the impact of hitting the
ground. As I was tending her, she began to struggle, as if she were mad,
or terribly afraid of something or someone. As I was pondering about the
condition of the woman, an invisible -something- hit me square in the chest,
knocking the air out of my lungs. I noticed that my skin was tingling at
the time, signaling that a woman as seizing Saidar. I guessed it to be the
woman, as she flew out of a Gate and all, so I shielded her. Seeing no
other alternative, I brought her to the Farm and placed her in the jail,
so that she may be questioned later.

*signed*
&amp;rDedicated Dreq Cypher&amp;n
</text>
